test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 169 == 13
 +  where 169 = <built-in function prod>([1, 13, 1, 13])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (1 == 3)
 +  where 1 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74fe00c3c840>([13])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74fe00c3c840> = [[1, 13, 1, 13, 1, 13], [1, 13, 1, 13, 1, 13], [13, 1, 13, 1, 13], [13, 1, 13, 1, 13], [1, 13, 1, 13], [1, 13, 1, 13], ...].count
